left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false

actor Student
boundary "Login UI" as B_Login
control "AuthController" as C_Auth
entity "CredentialStore" as E_Cred
entity "UserAccount" as E_User
entity "Session" as E_Session

Student --> B_Login : enter username/password
B_Login --> C_Auth : authenticate(credentials)
C_Auth --> E_Cred : validate password/hash
C_Auth --> E_User : load user/roles
C_Auth --> E_Session : create session/token
C_Auth --> B_Login : auth result
B_Login --> Student : show success/failure
@enduml
